lead_paragraph: Minnesota Vikings kicker Blair Walsh has been tight-lipped in recent days about the struggles that prompted the team to bring in free agents for tryouts this week.

headline.print_headline: Coach: Kicker Tryouts 'Lit a Fire' Under Vikings' Walsh
